About this item

    This fits your .
  • Make sure this fits by entering your model number.
  • Designed for Saving Charging and Sync Time: Lower resistance value pure copper wires inside ensures a maximum charging speed and transfer data up to 480 Mbits. Which obviously charge and sync faster than normal USB C 2.0 cables, and work better for tablets and quick charge devices.
  • Built to Last: Premium nylon braided exterior with pure copper wires inside and laser-welded putted on connectors for maximum reliability and durability. Up to 10,000+ bend and 8,000+ plugging and unplugging lifespan
  • Universal Compatibility: Perfect compatible with all current available USB C Devices - New Macbook, ChromeBook Google Pixel 2xl, Pixel C, Nexus 5X / 6P, OnePlus 2/3T, Galaxy S8/S8+/Note 8 /A5 2017, Huawei P9/P10, HTC 10/U11, Sony Xperia XZ, Lumia 950 / 950XL, LG G5/G6, Asus Zen AiO, Lenovo Zuk Z1, HP Pavilion X2, ASUS ZenPad S 8.0, New Nokia N1 tablet, and more.
  • PACK of THREE: These flexible 1m/1.5m/2m Durable and Tangle-Free USB C leads are ideal for a variety of everyday connection needs and highly portable.
  • Aluminum Shell - High-quality aluminum alloy shell, firmly connected, standard USB Type C port, even with a protective cover can be well fixed, can provide safer and more reliable charging.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Nitin
5.0 out of 5 stars Best value for money!
Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 16 December 2018
Verified Purchase
Following the demise of the charging cable supplied with my Samsung S9+, I came to Amazon for a suitable replacement. I came across this pack of 3 cables and considered them excellent value for money. When they arrived and were put to use, I knew immediately that I had made the right choice. First and foremost, they actually work and do exactly as they should. All three lengths charge at an enhanced as well as speedy rate. The fact that these come in three different lengths has proved to be very useful. One (the longest) is used by my bedside, so the phone can be charged while still being used. The shortest is perfect for the car. Finally, the third medium length cable is being used as a replacement for my wife's phone, since her original charging cable also gave up. For the money, these cables are very robust, excellent quality and work perfectly. Thanks!

Mike
5.0 out of 5 stars Very strong, high quality feel
Reviewed in the United Kingdom on 5 December 2019
Verified Purchase
I am always sceptical about "Heavy duty" and "Hard wearing" claims when it comes to cables. Afterall, we all know they are mostly short term disposable items that never last! But I have high hopes for these cables. They do feel very well made, strong and durable. They don't have the flexibility of thinner cables, not as much bend, but that's the trade-off you have to make if you want something that will last. Don't get me wrong, the bend is ok, but they are much stronger than conventional cables so will not do a tight right angle corner! The price for such a high quality product is amazing. Charging seems fast, not had a good test yet, but they certainly seem to have good power transfer so far. I would definitely recommend.
